"All *.amazonaws.com APIs; classified by action name (Delete*/Terminate* = destructive, Get*/List*/Describe* = read)." = "Toutes les API *.amazonaws.com ; classées par nom d'action (Delete*/Terminate* = destructif, Get*/List*/Describe* = lecture).";
